# Responses to 1 Major
1M 2N => 13+ hcp, 4+ M
1M 2M => 6-10 hcp, 3+ M
1M 3M => 11-12 hcp, 4+ M
1M 3m => 11-12 hcp, 6+ m
1M 1N => 11-12 hcp, 3 M

# Responses to a suit with a GF hand
1M NJy:down => 13+ hcp, 5+ y, longest_or_equal y among unbid
1M NJy => 13+ hcp, 4 y, longest_or_equal y among unbid

# 1/1
1H 1S:down => 6+ hcp, 4+ S

# Catch all
1M 1N => 6+ hcp
